Album: DrunkArtiste: ThundercatGenre: Jazz, Soul, Hip hop, R&amp;BRelease: February 24"Drunk" is Thundercat's third studio album. It is a fusion of intricate instrumentation/sound and incredible vocals from the American singer. The album features guest appearances from Michael McDonald, Kenny Loggins, Kendrick Lamar, Wiz Khalifa and Pharrell Williams. Essential tracks on the 23-track album include "Bus In These Streets," "Jethro," "Show You The Way," "Walk On By," "Friend Zone," "Drink Dat" and "The Turn Down". Thundercat has done an impressive job with this effort. He manages to bring together different genres and give a masterpiece.Star rating: 4 out of 5